[ Logger for IMAP-POP3 ]

1. Essential packages
   # perl -MCPAN -e shell
   cpan> install PKG_NAME 

   * lib, FindBin, Exporter
   * CGI, Net::POP3, Unicode::IMAPUtf7

2. Hierarchical directory 
   /logpool/HOSTS/s92/2007/10/23/local5
                  ^^^ ^^^^^^^^^^ ^^^^^^
                 Host Date       Filename

3. Edit config file
   # vi LoggerConfig.pm

4. Add your language and change the page style
   # vi cgi/CGIConfig.pm

5. Others
   Net::POP3         => POP3 check
   Unicode::IMAPUtf7 => decode IMAP mailbox name
